      <title>特朗普的“文化捍卫者”将重塑司法部民权部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[司法部民权部门几十年来一直致力于保护种族、民族、宗教少数群体以及妇女的权利——这些群体是美国非法歧视的最常见受害者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/trump-s-culture-defender-set-to-remake-doj-civil-rights-unit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 15:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西财政部下调修订财政计划中的储蓄预期</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/brazil-ministry-cuts-savings-estimate-from-revised-fiscal-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西参议院周五批准了缩减版的紧缩政策，随后巴西财政部下调了对总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦紧缩计划所节省预算的预测。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/brazil-ministry-cuts-savings-estimate-from-revised-fiscal-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 15:19:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西客车与卡车相撞 致38人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-22-people-die-in-a-crash-between-a-passenger-bus-and-a-truck-in-brazil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[圣保罗（美联社）——官员称，周六凌晨，巴西东南部米纳斯吉拉斯州一条高速公路上一辆客车与一辆卡车相撞，造成 38 人死亡。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-22-people-die-in-a-crash-between-a-passenger-bus-and-a-truck-in-brazil</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:55:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚圣诞节慈善活动发生踩踏事件 造成 13 人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-10-people-including-children-die-in-stampede-in-nigeria-at-a-christmas-charity-event</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿布贾，尼日利亚（美联社）——警方周六称，尼日利亚两起踩踏事件造成至少 13 人死亡，其中包括 4 名儿童，当时大批人群聚集在一起领取在一年一度的圣诞节活动中分发的食物和衣物。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-12-21/urgent-10-people-including-children-die-in-stampede-in-nigeria-at-a-christmas-charity-event</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:36:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>冰岛社会民主党就新政府达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/iceland-s-social-democrats-reach-deal-for-coalition-government</link>
      <description><![CDATA[冰岛新执政联盟同意限制预算以对抗通胀，并就继续进行欧盟加入谈判举行全民公投。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-21/iceland-s-social-democrats-reach-deal-for-coalition-government</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 21 Dec 2024 13:35:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
